<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Indian Actor - Shahid Kapoor</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
    <style>
        /* Professional CSS style for the title */
        .title {
            font-size: 2.5rem; /* Adjust font size as needed */
            color: #333; /* Dark text color */
            text-align: center; /* Center align the text */
            margin-top: 80px; /* Add space below the title */
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; /* Use a clean sans-serif font */
            font-weight: bold; /* Make the title bold */
        }

        /* Style for actor details */
        .actor-details {
            margin: 30px auto; /* Center the actor details */
            max-width: 600px; /* Limit width to improve readability */
            padding: 20px; /* Add padding for better visual appearance */
            background-color: #f9f9f9; /* Light gray background color for actor details */
            border-radius: 10px; /* Add rounded corners */
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* Add shadow for depth */
        }

        /* Style for actor image */
        .actor-image {
            width: 100%; /* Ensure the image fills the container */
            border-radius: 10px; /* Add rounded corners */
            margin-bottom: 20px; /* Add space below the image */
        }

        /* Style for actor name */
        .actor-name {
            font-size: 1.8rem; /* Adjust font size for actor name */
            color: #333; /* Dark text color */
            margin-bottom: 10px; /* Add space below the actor name */
        }

        /* Style for actor bio */
        .actor-bio {
            font-size: 1.2rem; /* Adjust font size for actor bio */
            color: #666; /* Dark gray text color */
            line-height: 1.5; /* Set line height for better readability */
            margin-bottom: 20px; /* Add space below the actor bio */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Include header partial with navbar -->
    <% include partials/header %>

    <!-- Main content for Indian Actor page -->
    <div class="container">
        <div class="actor-details">
            <img class="actor-image" src="/images/image3.jpg" alt="Shahid Kapoor">
            <h2 class="actor-name">Shahid Kapoor</h2>
            <p class="actor-bio">
                Shahid Kapoor is a versatile actor known for his exceptional performances in Bollywood. Born on February 25, 1981, in New Delhi, India, Kapoor made his acting debut in 2003 with the film "Ishq Vishk."
                <br><br>
                Kapoor gained widespread acclaim for his roles in films such as "Haider," "Kabir Singh," and "Udta Punjab." He has received several awards for his performances, including multiple Filmfare Awards.
                <br><br>
                Apart from acting, Shahid Kapoor is also a trained dancer and has showcased his skills in various dance sequences in his films. He continues to captivate audiences with his talent and dedication to his craft.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Include footer partial -->
    <% include partials/footer %>
</body>
</html>
